                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100718-38-off226 t18100718-38-cd227"></join>, a table spoon, value 12 s. a tea spoon, value 3 s. and a fork, value 12 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18100718-38-victim411" type="victimName">
                     William 
